data.description: Huge Corner-end unit, nearly New 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom with 1 car Garage Townhome! Huge Bonus comes with this particular chosen lot as it was Hand-picked from the Builder for its Preferred Location within the community, Side Yard, and Greenspace View! Super Central Orlando Location just down the street from the New $700-million Packing District project in College Park. 202 acres of Orlando’s Newest Built Entertainment area. Park Trails that will include a Food Hall managed by celebrity chef, Brewery, Farmers Market, YMCA (open), Orlando Tennis Center (open) and an outdoor Pavilion for Music and Events. Look up the details of Packing District Orlando! Preferred Large Corner-unit Townhome provides Large Lot Dimensions and a ton of Windows on 3 sides of the unit making it Light and Bright and most appealing with the beautiful exterior Architectural design and color pallet. Modern Kitchen with Bright-White Shaker Design Cabinets, Granite Countertops, Large Pantry, and Gorgeous Stainless-Steel Appliances! Large Open floor-plan with the Kitchen over-looking the Living area and a Large dimension Primary Bedroom, Bathroom and walk-in closet. Web-based AC Thermostat, Blinds throughout and a Samsung Front-Loading Washer and Dryer set are all included. Rear entry Private Garage with Web based automatic opener and private in garage 50Amp service for Electric Car charging. Landscaping is maintained by the HOA and there is a close by walking/jogging path and playground within the neighborhood. Additional parking and bike rack located just across from the unit. On the edge of Highly desired College Park Neighborhood with Boutique Shopping, Coffee Shops, Ice Cream/Soda Shop and Thriving Restaurants like the new Castle Irish Pub! Only 3 short miles into Winter Park or 4 miles to Downtown Orlando. Easy 423 access to Millenia Mall and the Theme Parks as well. Zoned for all Desired College Park Schools including “B” rated Elementary in 2023. This home is Move in Ready and in a Great Central Location! Act now on this Rare Find - Highly Desired Large Corner Lot and Preferred Location!
